2026-05-19T05:30:33.8906188Z 273            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-19T05:30:33.8906495Z 274            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-19T05:30:33.8906690Z 275            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-19T05:30:33.8907023Z 276            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-19T05:30:33.8907309Z 277            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-19T05:30:33.8907580Z 278            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-19T05:30:33.8907865Z 279            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
